description:
Like a circular, here's a new amber
Update of the rest of my life
Through all my projects
In the light of my ideas, small 10 seconds capture.
The news that pop on twitter, new prices, new adventures
A bottle to the sea,
sea of bottles, things and arts,
No water, no message...

And my circular NFT, which lets me write a few more words,
and maybe translate some feelings
